underlying_goal: The user wanted to commit recent changes related to paper specs and then push them to the main branch.
primary_success: Logically grouped unrelated file changes into two distinct, clear commits (archiving old specs vs. updating current ones).
brief_summary: The user requested to commit recent changes. Claude analyzed the modified files, identified two separate logical changes (archiving old specs and updating a comments document), created two distinct commits, and then successfully pushed them to the remote main branch upon user confirmation.
